whom the way of truth will be evil spoken of.</quote>  2 Pet. 2. 2. It is not these <lb/>
for whom we are Petitioners: But to those that are <normalised orig="faithfull" auto="true">faithful</normalised> to <lb/>
God and the King, that fear offending, that agree with you in all <lb/>
